 \text{Sp}(2n,\mathbb{C})=\{g\in\text{Mat}_{2n}(\mathbb{C})\mid J=g^TJg\}\quad\ where\quad J=\begin{pmatrix}  0 & 1_n \\  -1_n & 0  \end{pmatrix} 
 \text{sp}(2n,\mathbb{C})=\{g\in\text{Mat}_{2n}(\mathbb{C})\mid g^TJ+Jg=0\} 
